# ── Personal prep workspace (NEVER commit) ───────────────────────────────────
# This is where your resume, JDs, profile, stories, and generated artifacts live.
# It is generated per-user by `prep-intake`. Keeping it ignored means a clone of
# the plugin can never accidentally commit your personal data.
workspace/
prep/

# ── Secrets & local env ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
id_rsa
id_ed25519
credentials
*.pfx
*.p12

# ── Personal documents that must stay out of the shared repo ─────────────────
# (Belong only in the gitignored workspace; the secret-scan hook also guards these.)
*.pdf
*.docx
resume*
résumé*
cover-letter*
linkedin*.csv
linkedin*.zip

# ── Agent-first: keep the curated memory wiki, ignore the volatile staging buffer
.agent/memory/_staging.md

# ── OS / editor cruft ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log
.vscode/
.idea/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
